songs.title: Bury you
songs.lyrics:
I wasn't meant for this
I'm so sorry that I am the way I am
Cut my body open, make me whole again
I know you can
Yeah, I know you can

I'm so sorry I can't love
I promise I'm trying it won't be enough
I feel so much in my heart I'm empty at the same time
Empty at the same time
Always wanna fucking die
Will I make it through the night

I wasn't meant for this I'm so sorry that I am the way I am

Cut my body open, make me whole again
I know you can

Always wanna fucking die will I make it through the night
Will I make it
